# NSURLProtectionSpace proxy types

**API Collection**

These constants describe the supported proxy types used in [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/init(proxyHost:port:type:realm:authenticationMethod:)] and returned by [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/proxyType].

## Proxy types

- **NSURLProtectionSpaceHTTPProxy**: The proxy type for HTTP proxies.
- **NSURLProtectionSpaceHTTPSProxy**: The proxy type for HTTPS proxies.
- **NSURLProtectionSpaceFTPProxy**: The proxy type for FTP proxies.
- **NSURLProtectionSpaceSOCKSProxy**: The proxy type for SOCKS proxies.

## Identifying protection space properties

- **NSURLProtectionSpace protocol types**: These constants describe the supported protocols for a protection space, as returned by [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/protocol].
- **NSURLProtectionSpace authentication method constants**: Constants describing known values of the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/authenticationMethod] property of a [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace].
